ee http:<span class="comment">//bit.ly/CHEF-3255 for more information on the knife bug</span></span><br><span class="line">that causes <span class="keyword">this</span>.</span><br><span class="line">Successfully installed knife-solo-<span class="number">0.4</span><span class="number">.2</span></span><br><span class="line">Parsing documentation <span class="keyword">for</span> chef-<span class="number">12.0</span><span class="number">.0</span>.alpha<span class="number">.1</span></span><br><span class="line">Installing ri documentation <span class="keyword">for</span> chef-<span class="number">12.0</span><span class="number">.0</span>.alpha<span class="number">.1</span></span><br><span class="line">Parsing documentation <span class="keyword">for</span> chef-zero-<span class="number">2.2</span></span><br><span class="line">Installing ri documentation <span class="keyword">for</span> chef-zero-<span class="number">2.2</span></span><br><span class="line">Parsing documentation <span class="keyword">for</span> knife-solo-<span class="number">0.4</span><span class="number">.2</span></span><br><span class="line">Done installing documentation <span class="keyword">for</span> chef, chef-zero, knife-solo after <span class="number">20</span> seconds</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">3</span> gems installed</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
